akshya_Sen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lakshya_Sen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prannoy 21-12, 21-6.\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the women's singles on Aug 1, Singapore's world No.\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"20 Yeo Jia Min took on Japan's 10th-ranked Aya Ohori in a last-16 tie.\", \"from\": 3737, \"to\": 3807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3760, \"end\": 3765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9908125038238381, \"rank\": 0.006834866297507861, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3780, \"end\": 3789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aya_Ohori\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aya Ohori\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aya_Ohori\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aya_Ohori\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The result was unavailable at press time.\", \"from\": 3808, \"to\": 3849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[[nid:695790]]  Thisarticlewas first published inThe Straits Times.\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Permission required for reproduction.\", \"from\": 3919, \"to\": 3956, \"entities\": []}]}"